 He had always maintained the stand of Juche that calls for contributing to the cause of global independence through the successful Korean revolution based on the organic combination of the national duty and international duty in making revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He had steadfastly kept the revolutionary principle of independence against imperialism under any circumstances and always rendered disinterested assistance to the peoples of revolutionary and progressive countries. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
