 He also led the Korean people's great Fatherland Liberation War against the U.S. imperialist aggressors to victory and thus brought about the beginning of decline for the U.S. imperialists for the first time in history and opened up the era of new surge in the struggle against imperialism and the U.S. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Il Sung's historic exploits for global independence are now creditably being carried forward and glorified by Kim Jong Il who is identical to the President in ideology, leadership and personality.

