 It is the belief of the DPRK Olympic Committee that if the south side's Olympic Committee accepts the reasonable proposal of the north side, both teams of the north and the south will be able to participate in all international sports games as a unified team, a long-cherished desire of all the Koreans, and thus demonstrate the spirit and wisdom of the Korean nation.

